{"tid":1551031,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［黑色5毛警告]今晚嘅風向主題係_屌_柒_左_膠！！","createTime":"2019-09-07T20:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T21:18:43.000Z","uid":156582,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e91d6d6164ffa3ec9fd3ba70c7eb9cd8e1947fdd","tid":1551031,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:40:57.000Z","msg":"晚晚估領袖咁撚樣估你班柒頭吹乜野風，好悶呀，你班五毛有冇第二招架<br />\n<br />\n聽日美領人權法案集會，踩到上中共心口，所以今晚嘅風吹得最勁<br />\n<br />\n出面半版都係屌柒左膠post，大家快啲返正題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一，我明白有啲左膠係好撚累事，我都想你班左膠諗清楚自己做緊乜！<br />\n<br />\n二，聽日嘅活動先係重點，要行出嚟畀美國知我地唔收貨，五大訴求缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n三，不分化，勇武做乜都唔割，同時左膠幾柒都唔割！</span></span>"},{"pid":"23d21888ed63b26679d3c82857175ff972a61f26","tid":1551031,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:44:27.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"a999e11cb154f9813ebec2fa3fc7cca6d4d3e012","tid":1551031,"uid":274911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:45:31.000Z","msg":"不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2fc4fc11c8bfcff708b507d777af27da586413","tid":1551031,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:45:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集中推文宣Post同呢個Post</span>"},{"pid":"f7d1caa943ceee9ef4f2cbcbbbc66b8be5878b87","tid":1551031,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集中推文宣Post同呢個Post</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"70ebcf3fceb78197db770919b8dd8b536eef4502","tid":1551031,"uid":156582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:46:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">集中推文宣Post同呢個Post</span>"},{"pid":"d9fc628781d377bdad98afb775993492f80cf3cd"